<div class="nass margin-top-10"> <p><span id="p1" class="anchor"></span>هـ د ج<a href="#p1" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p2"></span><span class="c4">[٥٣٦٩ - هـ د ج]</span><a href="#p2" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p3"></span>هدَجَ يهدِج، هَدَجانًا وهَدْجًا، فهو هَدوج<a href="#p3" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p4"></span><span class="c5">• هدَج الشَّيخُ:</span> مَشَى متثاقلاً في ضعف وارتعاش، مشى بطيئًا <span class="c1">"هدَج الظَّليمُ"</span>.<a href="#p4" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p5"></span><span class="c5">• هدَجتِ الرِّيحُ:</span> صوَّتت.<a href="#p5" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p6"></span><span class="c5">• هَدَجت القِدرُ:</span> غلَتْ بشدَّة.<a href="#p6" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p> </div>